593
01:01:17,752 --> 01:01:19,513
<i>sangat membahagiakan.</i>

594
01:01:19,513 --> 01:01:23,295
<i>Kenapa? Kini kita
sudah sah menikah.</i>

595
01:01:23,295 --> 01:01:25,123
<i>Kita harus lebih baik
pada satu sama lain.</i>

596
01:01:25,123 --> 01:01:27,080
<i>Aku yakin istriku ingin
melakukan banyak hal...</i>

597
01:01:27,080 --> 01:01:28,789
<i>tapi ditahan karenaku.</i>

598
01:01:28,789 --> 01:01:31,010
<i>Menurutmu begitu?/ Apa?</i>

599
01:01:31,092 --> 01:01:32,800
<i>Apa kau bahagia?</i>

600
01:01:32,913 --> 01:01:34,131
<i>Aku bahagia.</i>

601
01:01:34,131 --> 01:01:35,917
<i>Ah-Jin! Ah-ram!</i>

602
01:01:36,225 --> 01:01:39,523
<i>Aku berharap hanya ada
kebahagiaan untukmu.</i>

603
01:01:39,523 --> 01:01:42,609
<i>Kau gila? Atau kau
benar-benar berselingkuh?</i>

604
01:01:42,609 --> 01:01:43,600
<i>Tidak...</i>

605
01:01:43,600 --> 01:01:46,373
<i>Dan kuharap
kau tak menderita karenaku.</i>

606
01:01:46,373 --> 01:01:47,573
<i>Aku minta maaf.</i>

607
01:01:48,858 --> 01:01:50,058
<i>Mohon...</i>

608
01:01:51,084 --> 01:01:52,284
<i>Selamat tinggal...</i>